Furfriends, we're so excited to finally share a pawsome group project, "Corgis for a Cause" 🐶 Introducing our 2018 Corgis for a Cause Calendar, a 14 month calendar that combines our two favorite things: corgis and philanthropy. Featuring some of the cutest corgs on Instagram & never-before-seen images, 100% of the calendar proceeds will be donated to @ASPCA. Our group was built on the shared goal of aiding people and their pets affected by recent natural disasters in the US. 
Calendar preorders are now available for purchase internationally at corgisforacause.com for $20 🗓 Your support for this worthy cause is greatly furpreciated. Woof woof! ✨
